    <item>
      <title>印度尼西亚监管机构在市场溃败之后简化股票回购规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/indonesian-regulator-eases-share-buyback-rules-after-market-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚的证券监管机构周三表示，它将允许公司未经股东大会的批准而回购股票，这一举动可以缓解本周痛苦的抛售后缓解紧张的举动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/indonesian-regulator-eases-share-buyback-rules-after-market-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 03:26:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BOFA警告中国股票更正在2015年重复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/bofa-warns-of-chinese-stock-correction-soon-in-2015-repeat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[BOFA Securities的战略家称，鉴于其与2015年的繁荣和萧条周期的相似之处，中国的股票集会可能会面临“有意义的更正”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/bofa-warns-of-chinese-stock-correction-soon-in-2015-repeat</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 02:54:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元释放后，Boj关注全球经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/yen-slightly-weaker-against-dollar-after-boj-holds-rates-steady</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日元对美元的日元削减损失，因为日本银行保持其政策利率稳定，并说工资和价格的良性周期正在加剧，同时密切关注全球贸易状况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/yen-slightly-weaker-against-dollar-after-boj-holds-rates-steady</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 02:34:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度计划钢铁关税12％，以防止“永久损害”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/india-plans-steel-tariffs-of-12-to-prevent-permanent-damage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度是世界第二大钢铁生产国，计划在大多数金属进口中施加12％的职责，这是一系列国家中最新的，以寻求对其国内行业的保护。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/india-plans-steel-tariffs-of-12-to-prevent-permanent-damage</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 02:33:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝恩资本拥有的桥数据获得了28亿美元的贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/bain-capital-owned-bridge-data-gets-record-2-8-billion-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士称，贝恩资本拥有的数据中心运营商桥梁数据中心为其在马来西亚的运营获得了28亿美元的贷款，这标志着其有史以来最大的银行融资协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/bain-capital-owned-bridge-data-gets-record-2-8-billion-loan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 02:11:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
